_Authentication failure page_

**Functional-Requirements**

- Displayed when the user is not authenticated or when API requests fail due to authentication errors
- Implemented as a separate error page with a dedicated route (e.g., /auth-error)
- Should provide a way for users to return to the login page

**Design-Requirements**

- Has a main text "ログインが必要です"
- Has a description text "ログインページはこちら" where "こちら" is a link. When clicked, it redirects to the login page (top page).
